    "The developed framework effectively removed the noise and also executed the forward prediction.",
    "The GP regression mechanisms were considered as the reference trajectory.",
    "The fuzzy-PLD mechanism was employed to analyze the robotic exoskeleton to compute the HMI.",
    "Later, prototype validations were executed to analyze various terrains without performing any transition over different measures.Liu et al.",
